inout.indexing

Class ArrayLexicon

  • java.lang.Object
    • inout.indexing.ArrayLexicon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Lexicon, java.lang.Iterable
    Deprecated. 
    Lexicon class for index-generation in Indexing. It's basically a very simple kind of Map, because the a index with is always incremented by one corresponds to a value. Was deprecated because - even though it is super simple - hashing with BiMap is so much faster!

    public class ArrayLexicon
extends java.lang.Object
implements Lexicon, java.lang.Iterable
    Author:
    Dennis Ulmer
